Key Match Events: Will Smith hit a tying, two-run homer and the Los Angeles Dodgers scored three more runs in the seventh to beat the San Diego Padres 7-2
Miscellaneous Highlights: This was the final game of the regular season series between the two teams, with the Dodgers winning 2-1
Others: The game took place at Dodger Stadium in Los Angeles, California, with an attendance of 52,433
